%h2 Events and Activities
%p
  In addition to many
  = succeed "," do
    %a{:href => "tournament_info.php"} tournaments
  game reviews and lessons by
  = succeed "," do
    %a{:href => "pros.php"} professionals
  the vendor area, and other Go-related activities, we also have
  these activities:
%p.notice
  All events, prices, and times subject to change.
%table.semantic.fullwidth.zebra
  %tbody
    - @arEventsByDate.each do |d,arEvt|
      %tr.date-header
        %th{:colspan => "7"}
          = d
      %tr.lesser-header
        %th Event
        %th Transport Departure Time
        %th Event Start/Arrival Time
        %th Price
        %th{:colspan => "2"}
      - arEvt.each do |e|
        %tr
          %td= e.evtname
          %td= e.evtdeparttime
          %td= e.evtstarttime
          %td= e.evtprice
          %td= link_to 'Edit', edit_event_path(e)
          %td= link_to 'Destroy', e, :confirm => 'Are you sure?', :method => :delete
%br/
= link_to 'New Event', new_event_path
